ROB_DRIVER_BODY_NAME: Driver
ROB_DRIVER_BODY_SUBTITLE: Arsenal Driver
PRIMARY_PISTOL_NAME: Pistol
PRIMARY_PISTOL_DESCRIPTION: A faulty prototype that can only fire a few shots.
PRIMARY_MACHINEGUN_NAME: Machinegun
PRIMARY_MACHINEGUN_DESCRIPTION: Fire rapidly for 120% damage per shot.
PRIMARY_RIOT_SHOTGUN_DESCRIPTION: Fire a shotgun blast dealing 8x140% damage.
PRIMARY_BADASS_SHOTGUN_DESCRIPTION: Fire a devastating shotgun blast for 24x140% damage.
PRIMARY_BAZOOKA_DESCRIPTION: Fire an explosive rocket for 600%-1,200% damage.
PRIMARY_ARMCANNON_DESCRIPTION: Fire a cannon shot for 1,000% damage.
PRIMARY_PLASMACANNON_DESCRIPTION: Fire a plasma shot for 1,200% damage.
PRIMARY_GOLEMGUN_DESCRIPTION: Fire a heavy shot for 800% damage.
PRIMARY_NEMMANDO_SWORD_DESCRIPTION: Slash enemies ahead with a sword for 160% damage.
PRIMARY_ARTI_GAUNTLET_NAME: Artificer's Gauntlet
PRIMARY_ARTI_GAUNTLET_DESCRIPTION: Fire a magma projectile for 350% damage.
SECONDARY_PISTOL_DESCRIPTION: Fire a secondary pistol for 500% damage.
SECONDARY_BASH_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Stun and push nearby enemies for 250% damage.
SECONDARY_ROCKETLAUNCHER_ALT_NAME: Rocket Launcher
SECONDARY_ROCKETLAUNCHER_ALT_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Fire a quick barrage of rockets for 250% damage each.
SECONDARY_HEAVY_MACHINEGUN_NAME: Heavy Machinegun
SECONDARY_HEAVY_MACHINEGUN_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Throw a grenade that stuns enemies for 800% damage.
SECONDARY_PLASMACANNON_NAME: Plasma Cannon
SECONDARY_PLASMACANNON_DESCRIPTION: Fire a charged plasma shot for 1,000% damage.
SECONDARY_BANDITREVOLVER_DESCRIPTION: Fire a high-caliber revolver for 1,500% damage.
SECONDARY_LUNARHAMMER_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. Fire a salvo of lunar fragments, dealing 180% damage each.
SECONDARY_NEMMANDO_DESCRIPTION: Fire dark projectiles for 240% damage.
SECONDARY_ARTI_GAUNTLET_DESCRIPTION: Fire a burst of ice magic for 600%-2,000% damage.
UTILITY_DASH_NAME: Dash
UTILITY_DASH_DESCRIPTION: Dash a short distance. You can hold up to 2 charges.
SPECIAL_SUPPLY_DROP_NAME: Supply Drop
SPECIAL_SUPPLY_DROP_DESCRIPTION: Request an airdrop of weapons.
SPECIAL_GRENADE_NAME: Grenade
SPECIAL_KNIFE_NAME: Knife
SPECIAL_KNIFE_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsUtility>Slashing</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Agile</style>. Slash enemies ahead for 470% damage.
SPECIAL_DRIVERCOIN_NAME: Driver Coin
SPECIAL_DRIVERCOIN_DESCRIPTION: Activate a special effect at the cost of coins.
ROB_DRIVER_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME: Default
ROB_DRIVER_PASSIVE_TOKEN: <style=cKeywordName>Focus</style><style=cSub>Focus greatly increases your damage output, but be careful not to be flanked while aiming.
ROB_DRIVER_ARSENAL_TOKEN: <style=cKeywordName>Arsenal</style><style=cSub>Switch between weapons using your primary and secondary abilities.
